---
// The homepage hero: a real Edgeworth box (Cobb–Douglas, computed — not sketched).
// Colors follow the Econschool notation layer: blue = person 1, red = person 2,
// green = Pareto set, orange = endowment & equilibrium, ochre = gains from trade.
---

