  <svg viewBox="0 0 480 340" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img"
    aria-label="Edgeworth box showing two agents' indifference curves through the endowment, the lens of gains from trade, the contract curve, and a competitive equilibrium on a budget line.">

